Difference compared to http://code.google.com/p/annovention/
* Discoverer can be specified to scan only classes, fields, or methods;
  and to scan only runtime visible or invisible annotations
* ClasspathDiscoverer has been improved to properly scan all class loaders
  (based on http://code.google.com/p/reflections)
* Apache Common Log has been removed

== Using with SBT

To use the stable version:

libraryDependencies += "tv.cntt" % "annovention" % "1.3"

To use the SNAPSHOT version:

resolvers += "Sonatype Snapshot" at "https://oss.sonatype.org/content/repositories/snapshots"

libraryDependencies += "tv.cntt" % "annovention" % "1.4-SNAPSHOT"
